## CRITICAL RULES - NEVER VIOLATE
1. curated_data/ is READ-ONLY. Never modify or delete.
2. s3://say2-4team/Colon_raw/ root parquet files (4 files) are EXCLUDED:
   - drug_features_catalog.parquet
   - drug_target_mapping.parquet
   - gdsc_ic50.parquet
   - lincs_drug_signature_normalized.parquet
3. Use ONLY these Colon_raw/ subdirectories: gdsc, depmap, lincs(GSE70138 only), drugbank, chembl, admet, cBioPortal, geo(GSE39582 only)
4. DO NOT USE: gtex, msigdb, opentargets, string (baseline first)
5. Protocol (code) = reuse Lung original. Data = Colon-specific only.
6. If proxy data needed, STOP and ask user.
7. If error occurs, STOP and report. Do NOT solve arbitrarily.
8. If uncertain, say "I don't know" and ask user.

## Subtype Tagging Policy
- For evaluation stratification: COAD/READ, MSI
- Metadata only (record but don't stratify): RAS, BRAF
- Skipped this round: HER2, CMS, sidedness

